              <li>Stand tall with your arms down by you side, but not touching their sides</li>
              <li>Elevate back leg until the thigh is parallel with the ground.</li>
              <li>Once stable look at the second hand on your watch, then close your eyes and see how long you can maintain balance. Any re-positioning of the foot is considered a loss of balance.</li>
